{"tid":2195588,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"［多次遭黨報譴責］反共桌遊《逆統戰》集資中","createTime":"2020-09-09T09:16:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T10:21:41.000Z","uid":211994,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"867d70ab184aec26142a058ef19679b220bad07f","tid":2195588,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T09:16:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.zeczec.com/projects/reversedfront\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zeczec.com%2Fprojects%2Freversedfront&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwgxY%2Fip2Wc62AYORpdIbS17M%3D&h=22164981\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.zeczec.com/projects/reversedfront</a><br />\n<br />\n<em>統一戰線</em>，共產黨術語，意指「聯合次要敵人，打擊主要敵人」。<br />\n<br />\n　　<strong>敵人的敵人，就是朋友。</strong><br />\n<br />\n　　逆統戰，就是「對共產黨逆向實施統戰」。聯合一切中共的敵人，打擊中共。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HUMpxrv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHUMpxrv.png&h=4f7c83a6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y2K6LMw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY2K6LMw.png&h=4abbd929&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《逆統戰》玩家扮演香港、蒙古、藏國、哈薩克、維吾爾、滿洲、臺灣和華夏反賊，發展抵抗組織、顛覆中共政權！<br />\n<br />\n※遊戲主地圖大致以原大清帝國的東西南北四界為止<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZwWEmjo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZwWEmjo.png&h=11fbe7df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">※《逆統戰》中集於2018年5月遭香港大公報與國臺辦譴責</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.takungpao.com.hk/hkol/topnews/2018-05/3569077_print.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.takungpao.com.hk%2Fhkol%2Ftopnews%2F2018-05%2F3569077_print.html&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwgxY%2Fip2Wc62AYORpdIbS17M%3D&h=85026bbb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.takungpao.com.hk/hkol/topnews/2018-05/3569077_print.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://paper.wenweipo.com/2018/05/17/YO1805170007.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpaper.wenweipo.com%2F2018%2F05%2F17%2FYO1805170007.htm&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwgxY%2Fip2Wc62AYORpdIbS17M%3D&h=47aea1a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://paper.wenweipo.com/2018/05/17/YO1805170007.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n陣容介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">香港（Hong Kong）&mdash;&mdash;1997年淪陷</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yr7L1kV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyr7L1kV.png&h=c01f6191&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n被清帝割讓的海港城邦<br />\n<br />\n　　原來是百越船民的漁村，在戰爭時投靠清帝的敵人英吉利，被英國建設成繁華的自由城，成為大陸通往世界的門戶。一百五十年後，在紅軍的逼迫下，英國把這座城市交給了紅軍，城邦自由逐漸淪喪，抗爭者在城市角落負隅頑抗。<br />\n<br />\n◆ 遊戲特色：進出口岸有限，但宣傳有優勢，而且是唯一可在牆內建立根據地的反共陣營<br />\n<br />\n◆ 可選根據地：香港城（即域多利城Victoria City，遊戲中代表港島中西區與灣仔區）；根據事件，有機會將根據地遷移至臺北、倫敦或卡加利<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><br />\n※圖板上有一個香港的小地圖，上面呈現了香港的各個區劃，讓玩家可以在遊戲中光復十八區。香港也可以在鄰近香港的牆內城鎮：澳門、廣州、深圳、湛茂發展組織。<br />\n<br />\n※香港女角（網友暱稱香港娘）在2018香港民族陣綫的粉專上，獲香港網友票選命名為Viya（Victoria的簡化）。圖片背景的廣式窗花代表「光復香港」，尖沙嘴鐘樓的大鐘代表「時代革命」，招牌的文字是「香港重光」（1945年8月15日香港脫離日軍高壓統治），男角的武器代表「香港人，報仇」。<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"de6ea183d74437bb39d12a391343661637eea7e6","tid":2195588,"uid":6618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T09:34:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07ae8906862ec366c7f06f06289498ed5dad8dc1","tid":2195588,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T10:04:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9373b3fabdd7fb0e072d0d249fe7b132217f83f1","tid":2195588,"uid":201740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T10:06:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0a796d5a4ef51df44dbf2d4148ed444b0307ddb","tid":2195588,"uid":282446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T10:15:19.000Z","msg":"個MV係幾型，佢出APP版或PC版會買黎玩"},{"pid":"588fbe0354953d8ee8680da839f3dfaa95014e0e","tid":2195588,"uid":364814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T10:17:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d4d1e99b349af1cac3a3969b7431c6edb0dadd3a","tid":2195588,"uid":36471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T10:17:38.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"23244bb77f54512ce9e71d626cc3430d2f65dd2b","tid":2195588,"uid":253608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T10:18:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb9d286dc6642cb99b9ae9145cd9f54ad84aa030","tid":2195588,"uid":235853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T10:21:41.000Z","msg":"sounds promising<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}